Step 4: Create the three required views
4.1 Layered View
View → New View → Layered → name Layered View.

Drag Business elements to the top, Application to the middle, Technology to the bottom.

Use the Mermaid diagram below for a reference layout.

Export as SVG: Exercise-2-<team-name>-layered.svg.

4.2 Application Cooperation View
View → New View → Application Cooperation → name App Cooperation.

Drag only Application components, services, processes, data objects, external services.

Show Serving, Composition, Access relationships.

Export: Exercise-2-<team-name>-cooperation.svg.

4.3 Technology Usage View
View → New View → Technology Usage → name Tech Usage.

Drag Technology nodes, system software, technology services.

Show Assignment, Serving, Flow.

Export: Exercise-2-<team-name>-technology.svg.
